<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.1.4">
<l>māṟu koṇṭuṭaṉ ṟetirntaval lavuṇaṉṟaṉ mārpaka mirupiḷavā</l>
<l>kūṟu koṇṭavaṉ kulamakaṟ kiṉṉaruḷ koṭuttava ṉiṭammiṭaintu</l>
<l>cāṟu koṇṭameṉ karumpiḷaṅ kaḻaitakai vicumpuṟa maṇinīḻal</l>
<l>cēṟu koṇṭataṇ paḻaṉama teḻiltikaḻ tiruvayin tirapuramē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of him who, having gouged into two the expanse of the chest</l>
<l rend="indent">of the powerful demon</l>
<l>Who opposed him, raging [and] bearing enmity, granted sweet grace</l>
<l rend="indent">to the son of his clan,</l>
<l>Is Tiruvayintirapuram where shines the beauty of the cool fields,</l>
<l rend="indent">full of mud in gem[-like] shade</l>
<l>Since juice-filled, soft, young sugarcane stalks, pressing [together]</l>
<l rend="indent">reach to the constraining sky.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
